1980年代是电子游戏业的第二个十年，电子游戏在这个年代经过大起大落。该年代初期正是街机界如日中天之时，1970年代后半段的巨头[[雅达利|雅达利]]等，仍然支配者市场。随着第三方游戏的过饱和，[[家用电脑|家用电脑]]的兴起，以及游戏品质的低劣，[[1983年美国游戏业萧条事件|北美游戏市场骤然崩溃]]，产业几近崩溃<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kvHcYe2sQ-I|title = The Video Game Crash of 1983|accessdate = 2015-09-16|archive-date = 2020-11-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201122134922/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kvHcYe2sQ-I|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

1983年，任天堂的[[红白机|红白机]]在日本发售。北美亦由街机时代转向游戏机时代，而填补空白的是红白机的美版Nintendo Entertainment System（NES）<ref name="gamespot.com">{{Cite web|url = http://www.gamespot.com/features/flashback-nes-6144735/|title = A 20-YEAR OLD LEGEND|accessdate = 2015-09-16|archive-date = 2012-11-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121110120947/http://www.gamespot.com/features/flashback-nes-6144735/|dead-url = no}}</ref>；但直到此时，投资者仍多认为电子游戏风潮已过<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://listverse.com/2011/12/08/top-10-embarrassing-moments-in-video-game-history/|title = Top 10 Embarrassing Moments in Video Game History|accessdate = 2015-09-16|archive-date = 2020-09-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200929165815/https://listverse.com/2011/12/08/top-10-embarrassing-moments-in-video-game-history/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。之后[[世嘉|世嘉]]和任天堂展开游戏机大战。任天堂亦于1989年推出畅销掌上游戏机[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.engadget.com/2010/05/07/nintendos-ds-family-becomes-best-selling-gaming-handheld-in-his/|title = Nintendo's DS family becomes best selling gaming handheld in history|accessdate = 2015-09-16|archive-date = 2019-06-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190613124123/http://www.engadget.com/2010/05/07/nintendos-ds-family-becomes-best-selling-gaming-handheld-in-his/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

